\section{Distributing GeoParquet}{

Following the OGC \emph{Best Practices for Distributing GeoParquet}, good defaults for distribution
are \code{ZSTD} compression at a moderate level, a row-group size around 50000-150000, the per-row
bounding-box covering columns enabled, and spatially ordered features:

